<h2>Creating a Puzzle</h2>
<div>
  <p>You can create your own nonogram for other players to solve. The game will automatically figure out the clues for you, all you need to do is draw it! Once your masterpiece is complete, add the name, and a cryptic hint (that will hopefully make sense after the the puzzle is solved). Choose a colour for it and save the nonogram. It will then be available to play if you create a new game.</p>
</div>